schools.name: Veterans Park Academy For The Arts

data.description: Motivated Sellers Beautiful 3/2/2 in need of little TLC but great starter home, located in the much sought after gated community of Marblebrook in Lehigh Acres. Across from Veterans Park, Features 1747 sqft home sits on an oversized fenced lake view lot and has a recent addition of a 20x40 screened lanai with attached Gazebo and 4 person hot tub not sure if working condition current owner never used! This adds an amazing 800sf of outside Florida living to enjoy watching beautiful sunsets that reflect off the lake, or enjoy a cup of coffee in the hot tub on a chilly morning. Additions also include an added 5x5 cook pad area just outside the screened area for your grill and/or favorite smoker, a screened in front door area. Eat-in kitchen with 3 beautiful bay windows has stainless steel appliances, double sinks, disposal, and little work needed on cabinets. Kitchen looks into the dining area and a nice sized great room. Master bedroom suite has ensuite with huge walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms are at opposite end of the house and share a 2nd full bathroom. Tile throughout except for bedrooms. Property is sold AS IS BRING OFFERS!
